Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經...兩個月...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許...差不多...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到極限了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了...看守的士兵...不見了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正...我也...都逃不掉嗎...？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒想過妳會救我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒問題嗎？我們在這種地方休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:01:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，要妳遇上痛苦的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來，妳坦白答我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為外表是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是甚麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由於 [儀式之日] 是神聖的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了舉行儀式的神帝和巫女之外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人會照慣例離開城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此連士兵也沒有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.26,0:01:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是最後一個舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能參予演出的演員人數是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚...甚麼人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我輕易便被忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或許也沒甚麼出場機會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繪...繪里子老師！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是神經過敏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽說過城堡內沒有人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一個人也沒有的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過只有神帝和巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.30,0:02:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女人就是巫女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦...內褲...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳...妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沾污巫女的皮膚是重罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何方神聖！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬君！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\bord2\fs32\fscy81\shad2}YU-NO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,字幕檔製作：Clive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四幕 [女神在世界的盡頭高歌]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊，妳平安便行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，給他們逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊，現在只須專心準備儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是，媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從昨晚起已經佈下結界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒理由能在城堡內自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能...吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.99,0:03:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在 DERA GROUND 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切事物由一名被稱為神帝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.25,0:04:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名被尊為神的少女口中的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的啟示來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是箇中的秘密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界的所有現象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能透過這裡的系統來控制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,換言之\N這個世界就像庭園中的盆景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但妳們沒辦法幫我脫身嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我叫過妳忍耐一下只穿內褲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這個世界有深遠關係的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會受到結界的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由活動的只有自己的肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，只穿內褲亦一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我帶來這個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這個世界沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸圍呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴胸圍對美容和健康有害\N是拓也告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了！那個蠢材呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想獨個兒靜一靜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬先生正拼死面對命運的擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭甚麼一切受命運主宰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得命運這個詞語
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包含了有某種關係的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它代表我不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等...等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看妳早晚會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的命運全看妳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎麼了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:55.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說過吧，跟這個世界有關的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會因應關係的深淺，而有相應程度的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有少許嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我流有這個世界的巫女的血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！做甚麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手...！救我...！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行...！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！爸爸...！爸爸...！不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終有一天能再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在報仇...之前...等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...！不要...！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快，我們很快便能見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬蒂亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要妳擔心，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好極了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.84,0:07:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這個世界的硬幣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前，我還小時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一個相同的硬幣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我記不起是誰送給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我一直當它是護身符好好保存
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我在後園玩耍時把它掉進井裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是妳跟這個世界的關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳身在這裡，果然是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不要去啊，那傢伙現在不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他很快便會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想馬上見他！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多話想跟他說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳會跟格蘭迪亞合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳現在只須專心完成那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那是YUNO的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO的出生是為了挽救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何想走進YUNO的心裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是...當時那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也...君！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君...是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於來到這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣...難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐...！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真遲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等你前來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽，妳認識這傢伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:09:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感動的重逢也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧，妳還有事情要去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽，告訴我，那傢伙是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論他是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的命運也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了，跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滾開！別阻住我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的對手是我啊，拓也君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，你記不起我是誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...豐富！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待我告訴你一件有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜妮絲她...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬君！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們不是親兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來無親無顧的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給前任名為姬蒂亞的巫女所收養
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她當我們是親兄妹一樣養大我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,澪...！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別阻頭阻勢！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫女要挽救世界一事，根本只是迷信！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒必要犧牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定能再見面，即使很短暫也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們給母子的關係連在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跟妳分開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有妳這個親人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬蒂亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.80,0:11:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟她再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懷著那個目的在世上流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至連次元也超越了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，當我好不容易找到她時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她以自己的性命換來你的出生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎？有馬敬子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你媽媽就是姬蒂亞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.70,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來到這個世界並非巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為你跟這個世界有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得到所有我想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的愛，她的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有，她的血！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嫉妒你是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有權奪去你的一切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把YUNO...還給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姬蒂亞的血！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了...我得到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的！是她的血！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想進一步感到她的溫暖！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了...姬蒂亞...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...馬上來...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個到...神帝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？她...格蘭迪亞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差少許...便接觸到她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那快點吧，沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君來到便無法繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.80,0:14:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓...也...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解釋給我聽！這是甚麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...先告訴我YUNO在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何那傢伙認識YUNO？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她...你認識的她...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不在人世
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切已經太遲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為...你來得太遲了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.25,0:14:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,廢話！答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO在哪裡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要欺負我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別阻住我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬先生，她就是YUNO小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO...是妳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YU...NO...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...是誰...？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO...根本不認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YU...NO...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不認識你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬君！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有馬君！振作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人是妳的爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸...爸...？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道...！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的事觸發儀式繼續嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO！繼續進行儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別管那種事，妳先伴在他身邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說比誰都更愛他的人是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去！YUNO！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳背負著全世界的命運啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對，為了全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！等等啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓妳妨礙她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波...波多乃小姐...！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃小姐！振作啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊\N這是...命運的...安排...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是命運...甚麼是命運啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能再見面...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能再見面...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們...給命運連在一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波多乃小姐...波多乃小姐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧，YUNO，快去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使喚來格蘭迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷史也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.95,0:17:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳怎會知道那種事！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浮游大陸 DERA GROUND 的設計者\N格蘭迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她所希望見到的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒理由...！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們現在面對的命運是人為的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點！妳快點去有馬君的身邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，如果YUNO不幹\N世界的命運便會...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求妳，聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他等待的人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能挽救他的心的...只有妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看，那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那間屋裡搬來了一對古怪的科學家夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很古怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們一看見我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[妳不是這個世界的人]\N便好像占卜師一樣地說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是，他的妻子長得很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來，他們的孩子快要出世了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸是個怎樣的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少許也好，我想妳告訴我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嗎？媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神奈正蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何一句也不告訴我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會等妳，媽媽，在未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先旨聲明，我很嚴厲的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是個傳統的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也...先生...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸...是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸...爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就像咒語，當我們再見面時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它會成為記認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜妮絲...！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對，是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格蘭迪亞...要走？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實她可能是最可憐的受害者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的！不是的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.80,0:21:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個結局不是我所希望的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切本來應該能夠重新開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算吧，已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好的...是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只顧自己找緊幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差點忘記重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下妳一個人...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也...君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞由美小姐...！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君...！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等...我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓也君...！！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經夠了，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不應該要妳背負起一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在無論做甚麼\N這個世界的命運，妳們也改變不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在...呼喚...我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她記起甚麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了成為巫女，她捨棄了內心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捨棄了最重要的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在根本沒可能會記起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們許下承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我記不起他的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須要去，我不想後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YUNO！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到...格蘭迪亞的聲音！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在呼喚YUNO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳要徹底負責任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是我的超等座位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼，這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指定座位...是美月小姐妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遲到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.20,0:23:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待亞由美幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒有睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.50,0:24:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學校...一起回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.40,0:24:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.80,0:24:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.80,0:24:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！澪，我聽到妳跟別人談話\N難道房裡有其他人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.50,0:24:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了！快點離開吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.70,0:24:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我怎樣離開這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從窗口走，快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.80,0:24:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是二樓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.80,0:24:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快點變得能讓我介紹給爸爸認識呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說過能再見面
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這隻戒指的咒語好像無效
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.80,0:25:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.99,0:25:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要妳久等了
